reviewText: ...is this an autographed copy or something with special bonus items?  I don't see something about that, but I'm just trying to figure out how it would be worth $60 USED when it's $25 on Jeanne's site!?!  I have seen parts of it online and she's funny as always.
Jeanne Robertson talks funny, moves funny, and all-around knows funny. If you think loud, frenetic, and profane equals comedy, this lady will show you a whole different way to laugh your head off.
